Gang-yeon?

597
00:43:57,373 --> 00:43:58,707
Kau pasti khawatir.

598
00:44:02,419 --> 00:44:03,879
Astaga.

599
00:44:43,252 --> 00:44:45,379
Kau bilang pernah berjanji pada Si-wan

600
00:44:46,046 --> 00:44:47,673
