614
00:45:48,943 --> 00:45:50,903
- Bagus.
- Bu, satu lagi.

615
00:45:50,986 --> 00:45:52,696
Baik. Selamat menikmati.

616
00:45:53,364 --> 00:45:54,239
Terima kasih.

